---
import Main from '../layouts/Main.astro';
import BeatmapCard from '../components/BeatmapCard.astro';
const pageName = 'Commission';
---
<Main currPage={pageName}>
    <div class="wrapper readable full-size">
        <h2>Commission</h2>
        <hr>
        <h3>Beat Saber Custom Map</h3>
        <img alt="header-commission-beat-saber" src="/assets/img/commission-beat-saber.jpg" loading="lazy"><br>
        <br>
        <p>
            I am Kival Evan, as you may recognise the name from certain ranked maps, playlists, etc. I have mainly
            crafted plentiful of Touhou Project arrangement map, including multiple set of genres. Take a look at
            the maps I've made.
        </p>
        <br><br>
        <div class="panel-center">
            <a class="link-button" href="https://beatsaver.com/uploader/5cff0b7798cc5a672c855af3">BeatSaver</a>
            <a class="link-button" href="https://bsaber.com/songs/new/?uploaded_by=kivalevan">BeastSaber</a>
            <a class="link-button" href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLp4N5ZtOuDZlhdvoH1INSPn2Qn9zrD19b">Video Preview</a>
        </div>
        <br><br>
        <p>
            I highly value quality of the map, you can expect well-refined mapping, high quality audio, and
            high definition cover image for both your content creation and enjoyment.
        </p>
        <br>
        <h4>Pricing & Payment</h4>
        <p>Rate is based on price per minute.<br>
            Rounded to next nearest minute, halved price for closest to next half minute.<br>
            <br>
            Payment made over PayPal with USD currency.<br>
            50% upfront, 50% upon delivery OR 100% upfront.
        </p>
        <br>
        <div class="panel-inner">
            <div class="panel-column">
                <h5>Mapping</h5>
                <ul class="list">
                    <li><strong>$20</strong> Mapper style</li>
                    <li><strong>$25</strong> Specific style</li>
                    <li><strong>$10+</strong> Additional difficulty</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-column">
                <h5>Lighting</h5>
                <ul class="list">
                    <li><strong>$15</strong> Handcrafted (non-Chroma)</li>
                    <li><strong>Free</strong> Lolighter (automated)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <p>
            <strong>NOTE:</strong><br>
            * Rate may increase depending on the complexity of the song, difficulty in map creation, or if it
            contain multiple (complex) BPM changes.<br>
            * Additional difficulty pricing depend on which difficulty, lowest starts at $10.
        </p>
        <br>
        <p>
            You may estimate cost <a href="/cost_estimator">here</a>, however pricing is subject to change.
        </p>
        <br>
        <h4>Enquiry</h4>
        <p>
            If you're interested in ordering a commission or have any question regarding the information, contact me
            on <a class="discord-popup" title="Kival Evan#5480" href="#">Discord</a>,
            <a href="https://twitter.com/Kival_Evan">Twitter</a>, or
            <a href="mailto:kivalevan@gmail.com">Email</a>.<br>
            <br>
            Please read <a href="#tnc">Terms & Conditions</a> for further information.<br>
            Once the order is made, you have accepted the Terms & Conditions.
        </p>
        <br>
        <h4 id="map-showcase">Map Showcase</h4>
        <span id='refresh-map'>Refresh</span>
        <div class="map-showcase">
            <BeatmapCard beatmapName="new world" />
            <BeatmapCard beatmapName="girly cupid" />
            <BeatmapCard beatmapName="frightmare" />
            <BeatmapCard beatmapName="the pressure" />
        </div>
        <br>
        <h4 id="tnc">Terms & Conditions</h4>
        <ul class="list">
            <li>I have the right to deny any commission.</li>
            <li>The map will be uploaded to my own BeatSaver account.</li>
            <li>Map will be released & uploaded as soon after completion and full payment made, but are allowed to
                request scheduled release.</li>
            <li>Song length depend on valid metadata if exist, otherwise use given source.</li>
            <li>Expected delivery time will be around 1-2 weeks but may vary depending on availability and option,
                I'll keep in touch showcasing progress and other related detail, you are allowed to give feedback on
                recent progress. Please do not spam or excessively remind me in short period of time.</li>
            <li>
                Lighting will take another considerable chunk of time. If you wish to receive the map sooner,
                consider switching to Lolighter option. Payment will be refunded or discounted by lighting cost if
                you swap the option.</li>
            <li><strong>Mapper Style:</strong> I have control of how I would map; this usually mean it will be top
                difficulty in mind. Revision is free but may be charged under <strong>Specific Style</strong> when
                it undergo multiple changes beyond the original scope. I will be the only judge if the change is
                significant enough to be charged differently.
            </li>
            <li><strong>Specific Style:</strong> you are free to decide what you need in the map, including
                but not limited to specific difficulty, note pattern you enjoy, etc. However, I have the right to
                refuse such requirement where it involve bad mapping practice,
                against my mapping habit, or anything I disagree with.</li>
            <li>Additional detail such as difficulty label, custom colour, platform, etc is allowed and free of
                charge. However, detail such as obscene text, similar coloured note, and other I
                disagree or deemed inappropriate will be rejected.
            </li>
            <li>I may not accept nor take request outside product listed here (such as curation, playlist, advert,
                etc), however it is negotiable.</li>
            <li>At any given time and reason, I may cancel the commission and you will receive full refund and
                disclosure for cancellation.</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <span><strong>NOTE:</strong> Terms & conditions is subjected to change.</span><br>
        <span>Last updated: 2021-03-19</span><br>
        <br>
        <div class="panel-center">
            <a href="#">Back to top</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</Main>

<style lang="scss">
    h2 {
        font-size: 3rem;
    }
    h3 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
    img {
        width: 100%;
        box-shadow: 0 0.25em 0.5em black;
    }
    .panel-center {
        margin: auto;
        text-align: center;
    }
    .panel-inner {
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
    }
    .panel-input {
        width: 100%;
    }
    .panel-input input[type='checkbox'] {
        width: 1.5em;
        height: 1.5em;
        margin: 0.25em;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    .panel-input label {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 1.0625rem;
        padding-left: 0.5em;
        margin-left: -0.5em;
        margin-top: 0.25em;
        cursor: pointer;
        vertical-align: top;
    }
    .panel-column {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 50%;
    }
    .link-button {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        font-weight: bold;
        padding: 0.75em 0.75em;
        margin: 0 0.25em;
        border: 0.125em solid #111;
        border-radius: 0.75em;
        background-color: #282828;
        transition: background-color 0.25s ease;
        &:hover {
            background-color: #202020;
        }
    }
    ul {
        padding: 0;
        list-style-type: none;
    }
    .list li {
        margin: 0.625em 0;
        line-height: 1.25em;
        text-align: justify;
        &::before {
            content: '\00BB';
            margin-right: 0.5em;
        }
    }
    #refresh-map {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #37f;
        transition: color ease 0.125s;
    }
    #refresh-map:hover {
        color: #f00;
        cursor: pointer;
    }
    p {
        margin: 0.25em 0;
        text-align: justify;
    }
</style>
